\section{Load and plot data}
Load FDboost package.
<<pkg-attach, echo = FALSE, fig=FALSE>>=
library(FDboost)
@

Load data and compute the first derivative.
<<load-data, echo = TRUE>>=
data(fuelSubset)
fuel <- fuelSubset
str(fuel)

